description: Learn pearls of information about how to stay healthy. Living Healthy coaches people on topics like colon and breast cancer screening, tips for losing weight, getting better control of your diabetes, and quitting smoking. Living Healthy isn't a substitute for a doctor and shouldn't be used as medical advice. Living Healthy empowers you to have these conversations with your own doctor.
name: Living Healthy
shortDescription: Learn how to stay healthy and take the best care of yourself possible.
